<li id="cite_note-15"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.physorg.com/news5890.html" class="external text" title="http://www.physorg.com/news5890.html" rel="nofollow">Researchers produce strong, transparent carbon nanotube sheets</a></li>
