<li><a href="http://global-energy-system.pbwiki.com" class="external text" title="http://global-energy-system.pbwiki.com" rel="nofollow">Concept for using a solar sail to simultaneously provide a Global Energy System and a Weather Control System.</a></li>
</ul>


